# @param {Integer} purchase_amount
# @return {Integer}
def account_balance_after_purchase(purchase_amount)
    # Calculate the rounded amount
    rounded_amount = if purchase_amount % 10 < 5
                       (purchase_amount / 10) * 10
                     else
                       (purchase_amount / 10 + 1) * 10
                     end

    # Calculate the final account balance
    100 - rounded_amount
end
